{"tid":2180760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★社區組織：九成半貧窮學童對在家開學感到不開心 因家中缺乏電腦","createTime":"2020-08-30T06:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T05:53:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6142b3e82e85e937b1df8cc3953e37b812a97025","tid":2180760,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社區組織協會調查發現，逾九成半貧窮學童對在家開學感到無奈或不開心。<br />\n<br />\n社協在八月底以問卷訪問730名基層學童，九成受訪學童指，過去七個月，因上網及家庭環境限制令學習無成效；有四成學生表示，家中缺乏可以上網的電腦。<br />\n<br />\n社協認為在疫情下，學生對網上學習需求上升，促請教育局完善資助清貧學童購買電腦的計劃，並提供上網費實報實銷，又建議安排有上網困難的學生回校學習。<br />\n<br />\n梁同學：「我不懂的時候問老師，我打字很慢，又不懂打字，有時候跳過問題，再問（老師）又不好意思，因為已經說完了，再問，老師會說『為甚麼你聽不清楚？』」<br />\n<br />\n家長陳女士：「學校有提供數據卡，但很少流量，只有5GB，視像（上課）很快就用完了，所以沒辦法，上不到課。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=403656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403656&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=8fb303bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403656&h=95da12ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=403656</a>"},{"pid":"de66ab22fc6e72efbe58cb4231cb584c5b8ddc97","tid":2180760,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">家中缺乏 $$$$</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa46e6502226fae88db3e4305637b13421ca62c","tid":2180760,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">窮人生仔</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c6d348afb7ebe262823c1b0c5793110aa7c03fe1","tid":2180760,